room_title: Escape room "Through The Looking Glass" by The Escape South Florida in West Palm Beach
room_address: 10800 N. Military Trail Suite 211 Palm Beach Gardens, FL 33410
room_description: Alice has dreamt of Wonderland before but this time she’s not sure it's a dream at all. Journey with her through this whimsical world, where not everything is always as it seems. Up may be down and left may be right but don’t let your senses mislead you. Your task is to help Alice find her way out of Wonderland before it’s too late, the clock is ticking…
